00:00:06.173 --> 00:00:07.709 position:10% line:89% align:start
[opening theme song playing]

00:01:47.174 --> 00:01:49.142 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunts]
-[grunts]

00:01:49.644 --> 00:01:50.745 position:27% line:89% align:start
[labored breath]

00:01:51.646 --> 00:01:53.213 position:35% line:89% align:start
This is...

00:01:53.246 --> 00:01:54.882 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] Looks like
you're finally awake.

00:01:56.050 --> 00:01:58.753 position:16% line:83% align:start
Was everything we've seen
before a dream?

00:01:58.786 --> 00:02:01.956 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah. To distract us from
being dissolved...

00:02:01.990 --> 00:02:03.658 position:33% line:89% align:start
in this room.

00:02:03.691 --> 00:02:05.292 position:16% line:89% align:start
Break the door. Quickly.

00:02:05.793 --> 00:02:06.861 position:30% line:89% align:start
Use your power.

00:02:07.528 --> 00:02:08.730 position:30% line:89% align:start
Star Platinum!

00:02:10.598 --> 00:02:11.833 position:41% line:89% align:start
Do it!

00:02:12.734 --> 00:02:13.601 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ora!

00:02:14.134 --> 00:02:15.603 position:35% line:89% align:start
[crackling]

00:02:17.471 --> 00:02:20.041 position:35% line:83% align:start
It's open!
Pull me out of here!

00:02:20.074 --> 00:02:21.809 position:27% line:83% align:start
We have to leave
this room right away!

00:02:22.543 --> 00:02:23.945 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Jotaro] Hold on.

00:02:23.978 --> 00:02:25.913 position:33% line:83% align:start
What was that
you said just now?

00:02:25.947 --> 00:02:27.982 position:33% line:83% align:start
Did you say,
"Star Platinum"?

00:02:28.016 --> 00:02:29.216 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's my Stand.

00:02:31.019 --> 00:02:33.186 position:27% line:83% align:start
Jolyne, how would
you know that?

00:02:33.988 --> 00:02:35.188 position:21% line:89% align:start
From what I can tell,

00:02:35.222 --> 00:02:36.591 position:19% line:89% align:start
it only became reality

00:02:36.624 --> 00:02:38.760 position:27% line:83% align:start
after I told you
about Johngalli A.

00:02:39.259 --> 00:02:41.095 position:30% line:89% align:start
In other words,

00:02:41.129 --> 00:02:44.132 position:13% line:83% align:start
there's no way you could've
seen my power yet.

00:02:44.164 --> 00:02:45.667 position:27% line:83% align:start
Even if you feel
its existence

00:02:45.700 --> 00:02:47.234 position:19% line:89% align:start
since you're my child,

00:02:47.267 --> 00:02:48.670 position:30% line:83% align:start
there's no way
you should know

00:02:48.703 --> 00:02:49.871 position:16% line:89% align:start
the name "Star Platinum."

00:02:52.907 --> 00:02:54.474 position:13% line:89% align:start
That would be inconsistent!

00:02:57.377 --> 00:02:59.514 position:19% line:89% align:start
This... isn't reality!

00:03:06.087 --> 00:03:07.320 position:33% line:89% align:start
[sudden gasp]

00:03:08.056 --> 00:03:08.923 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne groans]

00:03:09.657 --> 00:03:11.592 position:27% line:89% align:start
Stone... Ocean...

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:13.928 position:41% line:89% align:start
Jolyne.

00:03:13.961 --> 00:03:15.295 position:35% line:89% align:start
About time.

00:03:15.328 --> 00:03:17.131 position:24% line:83% align:start
You finally snapped
out of it.

00:03:17.165 --> 00:03:19.067 position:21% line:89% align:start
I had to push myself.

00:03:19.100 --> 00:03:20.935 position:10% line:89% align:start
My thread dissolves so fast.

00:03:20.968 --> 00:03:22.202 position:38% line:89% align:start
Jolyne...

00:03:22.804 --> 00:03:24.105 position:19% line:89% align:start
Were you dreaming too?

00:03:24.138 --> 00:03:26.841 position:10% line:89% align:start
No, I've been in a nightmare.

00:03:26.874 --> 00:03:28.643 position:7% line:89% align:start
Then I woke up to all of this.

00:03:29.177 --> 00:03:30.511 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yes, I see.

00:03:30.545 --> 00:03:33.781 position:19% line:83% align:start
Looks like we were both
being shown specific visions.

00:03:33.815 --> 00:03:35.083 position:16% line:89% align:start
Like watching a movie...

00:03:35.116 --> 00:03:36.483 position:33% line:89% align:start
Sounds right.

00:03:36.517 --> 00:03:39.386 position:10% line:83% align:start
If only we had some popcorn,
it'd be perfect.

00:03:39.419 --> 00:03:41.254 position:21% line:89% align:start
I can't move anymore.

00:03:41.288 --> 00:03:43.124 position:30% line:89% align:start
Not a finger...

00:03:43.157 --> 00:03:45.325 position:30% line:83% align:start
What about you?
Can you move?

00:03:45.358 --> 00:03:47.360 position:21% line:83% align:start
The current situation
could be a dream...

00:03:48.062 --> 00:03:49.396 position:21% line:89% align:start
within another dream.

00:03:50.531 --> 00:03:53.467 position:16% line:83% align:start
If you can't move at all,
then it's reality.

00:03:54.168 --> 00:03:56.104 position:27% line:89% align:start
A harsh reality.

00:03:56.137 --> 00:03:57.772 position:24% line:83% align:start
One which we might
not escape.

00:03:57.805 --> 00:03:58.673 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yes, I see.

00:03:58.706 --> 00:04:01.976 position:10% line:83% align:start
At this rate, we're screwed.
Dead meat.

00:04:02.877 --> 00:04:04.946 position:13% line:89% align:start
The power of the pendant...

00:04:04.979 --> 00:04:07.782 position:16% line:83% align:start
Bring out the Stand that
you just used to wake me up.

00:04:09.016 --> 00:04:10.585 position:33% line:89% align:start
Stone Ocean?

00:04:10.618 --> 00:04:11.686 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:04:11.719 --> 00:04:13.420 position:21% line:83% align:start
Can you bring it out
in a clump?

00:04:13.453 --> 00:04:14.956 position:13% line:89% align:start
Basically, your strength...

00:04:14.989 --> 00:04:17.592 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's no good. I know that.

00:04:17.625 --> 00:04:20.128 position:24% line:83% align:start
It took everything
I had just to wake you.

00:04:20.161 --> 00:04:21.863 position:13% line:83% align:start
There's no hope of opening
the door.

00:04:21.896 --> 00:04:22.864 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's fine.

00:04:22.897 --> 00:04:23.865 position:24% line:89% align:start
Just bring it out.

00:04:23.898 --> 00:04:25.032 position:38% line:89% align:start
[inhales]

00:04:25.066 --> 00:04:25.933 position:38% line:89% align:start
[exhales]

00:04:26.868 --> 00:04:28.603 position:13% line:89% align:start
[fast piano music playing]

00:04:29.670 --> 00:04:30.838 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes, like that.

00:04:31.606 --> 00:04:32.472 position:35% line:89% align:start
Keep going.

00:04:33.207 --> 00:04:35.109 position:10% line:89% align:start
Can you bring it out further?

00:04:35.143 --> 00:04:36.644 position:27% line:89% align:start
Just a bit more.

00:04:36.677 --> 00:04:38.846 position:16% line:83% align:start
Bring it a little closer
to me.

00:04:39.881 --> 00:04:41.015 position:16% line:89% align:start
It would be for the best

00:04:41.048 --> 00:04:43.684 position:13% line:83% align:start
if you could shift it over
a little further to my left.

00:04:44.886 --> 00:04:46.353 position:27% line:89% align:start
That should work.

00:04:46.386 --> 00:04:49.422 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's not what I'd call ideal,
but it's close.

00:04:49.456 --> 00:04:51.826 position:21% line:83% align:start
This should at least
help us get out of here.

00:04:53.227 --> 00:04:55.328 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[focused grunt]
-Ora!

00:04:55.730 --> 00:04:56.597 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:04:59.700 --> 00:05:02.435 position:27% line:89% align:start
[light crackling]

00:05:02.469 --> 00:05:05.506 position:19% line:83% align:start
That was Star Platinum.
It's my Stand.

00:05:06.207 --> 00:05:07.642 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now then, pull me out.

00:05:07.675 --> 00:05:09.877 position:27% line:83% align:start
This is reality.
Make no mistake.

00:05:09.911 --> 00:05:11.879 position:30% line:89% align:start
You... bastard.

00:05:12.914 --> 00:05:15.149 position:24% line:89% align:start
[grunts] Damn you!

00:05:15.183 --> 00:05:16.551 position:35% line:89% align:start
That hurt!

00:05:16.584 --> 00:05:19.654 position:27% line:83% align:start
This pain I feel,
and this irritation...

00:05:20.353 --> 00:05:22.355 position:19% line:89% align:start
Bastard. How dare you?

00:05:23.057 --> 00:05:25.726 position:10% line:89% align:start
This irritation I'm feeling!

00:05:25.760 --> 00:05:27.762 position:30% line:83% align:start
There's no way
this can be a hallucination!

00:05:28.830 --> 00:05:31.331 position:21% line:89% align:start
[grunting in effort]

00:05:33.935 --> 00:05:36.436 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:05:38.306 --> 00:05:40.007 position:19% line:89% align:start
Good. Lift your hands.

00:05:40.875 --> 00:05:41.976 position:30% line:89% align:start
What is it now?

00:05:42.543 --> 00:05:43.544 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ora!

00:05:46.147 --> 00:05:47.048 position:38% line:89% align:start
Let's go.

00:05:47.815 --> 00:05:48.816 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, right...

00:05:50.184 --> 00:05:52.286 position:16% line:89% align:start
Do you know what this is?

00:05:52.320 --> 00:05:54.655 position:30% line:83% align:start
Whatever it is,
we were saved because of it.

00:05:55.422 --> 00:05:56.657 position:21% line:89% align:start
That's a human bone.

00:05:56.691 --> 00:05:57.325 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:05:57.357 --> 00:05:58.491 position:38% line:89% align:start
Further,

00:05:58.526 --> 00:06:00.493 position:16% line:83% align:start
it's a part of the pelvis
called the sacrum,

00:06:00.528 --> 00:06:01.996 position:21% line:89% align:start
from an adult female.

00:06:02.029 --> 00:06:03.531 position:38% line:83% align:start
Based on
the surface condition,

00:06:03.564 --> 00:06:04.832 position:27% line:83% align:start
it seems to have
been dissolved

00:06:04.866 --> 00:06:06.167 position:21% line:89% align:start
by some kind of acid.

00:06:06.200 --> 00:06:07.602 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's been dissolved?

00:06:07.635 --> 00:06:09.369 position:16% line:89% align:start
You mean, the same stuff?

00:06:09.402 --> 00:06:10.037 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who knows?

00:06:10.571 --> 00:06:11.672 position:24% line:89% align:start
I have no clue why

00:06:11.706 --> 00:06:13.274 position:35% line:83% align:start
you'd carry
something like that around,

00:06:13.307 --> 00:06:14.542 position:21% line:83% align:start
but it doesn't matter
right now.

00:06:14.575 --> 00:06:16.510 position:24% line:83% align:start
I was the only one
who saw him,

00:06:16.544 --> 00:06:18.112 position:24% line:89% align:start
but the kid exists.

00:06:18.145 --> 00:06:19.213 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's a mystery,

00:06:19.247 --> 00:06:21.349 position:27% line:83% align:start
but this is proof
that he's actually here!

00:06:21.381 --> 00:06:22.783 position:30% line:89% align:start
[alarm blaring]

00:06:22.817 --> 00:06:23.885 position:35% line:89% align:start
[both gasp]

00:06:23.918 --> 00:06:26.787 position:21% line:83% align:start
[woman over speaker]
Code 909. Security level four.

00:06:26.821 --> 00:06:29.523 position:21% line:83% align:start
Abnormality detected
outside the visiting room.

00:06:29.557 --> 00:06:32.093 position:5% line:89% align:start
Security level four. Code 909...

00:06:32.126 --> 00:06:33.594 position:21% line:89% align:start
What are we gonna do?

00:06:33.628 --> 00:06:35.096 position:33% line:83% align:start
Because once
we left that room,

00:06:35.129 --> 00:06:36.496 position:10% line:89% align:start
you became a wanted criminal.

00:06:36.530 --> 00:06:38.332 position:13% line:89% align:start
Like I said from the start,

00:06:38.366 --> 00:06:40.400 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm getting you out of here.

00:06:40.433 --> 00:06:42.737 position:24% line:83% align:start
You have it, right?
The pendant?

00:06:44.972 --> 00:06:47.508 position:13% line:83% align:start
That thing's more important
than it looks,

00:06:47.541 --> 00:06:48.776 position:27% line:89% align:start
so don't lose it.

00:06:50.344 --> 00:06:52.046 position:16% line:89% align:start
Now then, break-out time.

00:07:01.222 --> 00:07:03.357 position:16% line:89% align:start
[male voice sighs deeply]

00:07:03.391 --> 00:07:06.994 position:16% line:83% align:start
I never would've guessed
they'd escape my trap.

00:07:11.431 --> 00:07:13.768 position:27% line:83% align:start
Not many guards.
What's that about?

00:07:13.801 --> 00:07:15.703 position:13% line:89% align:start
This is a semi-public area.

00:07:17.470 --> 00:07:18.539 position:33% line:89% align:start
Take a look.

00:07:20.841 --> 00:07:23.077 position:21% line:83% align:start
Our goal is a window
at the western wall.

00:07:24.312 --> 00:07:26.113 position:21% line:83% align:start
The window faces out
to the shore,

00:07:26.147 --> 00:07:26.948 position:13% line:89% align:start
and from there we'll escape

00:07:26.981 --> 00:07:29.317 position:21% line:83% align:start
to the outside world
via submarine.

00:07:29.350 --> 00:07:31.018 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] A submarine?

00:07:31.052 --> 00:07:33.354 position:13% line:83% align:start
I have a little connection
with the organization

00:07:33.387 --> 00:07:35.656 position:21% line:83% align:start
called the Speedwagon
Foundation.

00:07:35.690 --> 00:07:37.191 position:13% line:89% align:start
They've arranged it for us.

00:07:40.361 --> 00:07:44.231 position:21% line:89% align:start
[banging in distance]

00:07:44.999 --> 00:07:45.967 position:24% line:89% align:start
[exhales nervously]

00:07:49.103 --> 00:07:51.639 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm not seeing any cameras
in this hallway.

00:07:51.672 --> 00:07:55.042 position:10% line:83% align:start
The window is just down this
junction here to the left.

00:07:55.076 --> 00:07:58.012 position:10% line:83% align:start
From the window to the shore
is just under 20 meters.

00:07:58.045 --> 00:08:00.715 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm sure you have a lot
on your mind right now,

00:08:00.748 --> 00:08:03.250 position:21% line:83% align:start
but we have to focus
on getting outside.

00:08:03.284 --> 00:08:04.418 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Star Platinum] Ora!

00:08:04.452 --> 00:08:05.519 position:38% line:89% align:start
Let's go.

00:08:10.024 --> 00:08:11.726 position:35% line:89% align:start
[rumbling]

00:08:12.326 --> 00:08:13.761 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, it was that fan.

00:08:14.161 --> 00:08:15.029 position:41% line:89% align:start
Jolyne.

00:08:18.299 --> 00:08:19.700 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yelps]

00:08:19.734 --> 00:08:22.003 position:10% line:89% align:start
[intense piano music playing]

00:08:25.006 --> 00:08:25.973 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:08:26.007 --> 00:08:27.908 position:21% line:89% align:start
[grimaces] It hurts!

00:08:27.942 --> 00:08:29.944 position:19% line:83% align:start
Where were you looking?
Don't rush.

00:08:31.045 --> 00:08:32.279 position:30% line:89% align:start
Here, stand up.

00:08:34.048 --> 00:08:36.217 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[soft piano music playing]
-[speechless]

00:08:37.451 --> 00:08:39.520 position:19% line:89% align:start
Go ahead. Take my hand.

00:08:39.553 --> 00:08:42.923 position:10% line:89% align:start
Uh... I'm okay, just clumsy.

00:08:42.957 --> 00:08:43.824 position:30% line:89% align:start
But thank you.

00:08:43.858 --> 00:08:46.293 position:16% line:83% align:start
I can stand up on my own
without any help.

00:08:46.327 --> 00:08:47.461 position:30% line:89% align:start
That isn't it.

00:08:47.495 --> 00:08:48.596 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's this.

00:08:48.629 --> 00:08:50.631 position:21% line:83% align:start
Be more careful when
you trip next time.

00:08:50.664 --> 00:08:53.000 position:16% line:83% align:start
What are you going to do
if this flies away,

00:08:53.034 --> 00:08:53.834 position:30% line:89% align:start
or you lose it?

00:08:55.236 --> 00:08:57.204 position:21% line:89% align:start
[grunts in disbelief]

00:08:57.238 --> 00:08:58.706 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's wrong?

00:08:58.739 --> 00:09:00.274 position:35% line:83% align:start
I told you
this was important,

00:09:01.108 --> 00:09:02.810 position:19% line:89% align:start
so hold on to it. Here.

00:09:02.843 --> 00:09:05.046 position:16% line:89% align:start
[emotional music playing]

00:09:07.214 --> 00:09:08.616 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're really going to Tokyo

00:09:08.649 --> 00:09:10.017 position:24% line:83% align:start
despite everything
our daughter

00:09:10.051 --> 00:09:11.786 position:19% line:83% align:start
is having to go through
right now?

00:09:11.819 --> 00:09:13.387 position:10% line:89% align:start
What kind of father are you?

00:09:13.421 --> 00:09:15.289 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[phone clicks]
-Hello? Hello?

00:09:20.895 --> 00:09:22.863 position:21% line:83% align:start
You haven't changed,
have you?

00:09:22.897 --> 00:09:24.632 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're always thinking
everything through

00:09:24.665 --> 00:09:26.033 position:21% line:89% align:start
calmly and logically.

00:09:26.067 --> 00:09:28.702 position:13% line:83% align:start
Even when I was a kid dying
of a high fever,

00:09:28.736 --> 00:09:30.838 position:16% line:83% align:start
you couldn't be bothered
to come for see me.

00:09:30.871 --> 00:09:32.640 position:24% line:83% align:start
Or when I was doing
a little joy-riding,

00:09:32.673 --> 00:09:34.341 position:24% line:83% align:start
and they accused me
of stealing the car.

00:09:35.176 --> 00:09:36.310 position:19% line:89% align:start
You were on an airplane

00:09:36.343 --> 00:09:38.813 position:27% line:83% align:start
heading somewhere
exotic instead.

00:09:38.846 --> 00:09:41.816 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yet somehow, I still
grew up safe and healthy.

00:09:42.683 --> 00:09:45.119 position:13% line:89% align:start
[emotional music continues]

00:09:45.152 --> 00:09:47.021 position:13% line:83% align:start
[in sarcastic tone] I mean,
I'm a troublemaker that

00:09:47.054 --> 00:09:49.623 position:13% line:83% align:start
doesn't get hurt no matter
how many times I fall!

00:09:49.657 --> 00:09:51.792 position:24% line:89% align:start
So lucky! Woo-hoo!

00:09:51.826 --> 00:09:54.295 position:10% line:83% align:start
-What are you going on about?
-[irritated grunt]

00:09:56.097 --> 00:09:58.299 position:24% line:83% align:start
If it's important,
hold onto it yourself!

00:09:58.966 --> 00:10:00.067 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grumbles]

00:10:00.101 --> 00:10:01.068 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Jolyne.
-Shut up.

00:10:01.102 --> 00:10:03.437 position:19% line:83% align:start
-It's a bit late for--
-Not that.

00:10:03.471 --> 00:10:05.739 position:16% line:89% align:start
Have you not noticed yet?

00:10:05.773 --> 00:10:08.375 position:24% line:83% align:start
Something has been
following us. Quietly.

00:10:09.076 --> 00:10:10.377 position:27% line:89% align:start
Jolyne, get down.

00:10:10.411 --> 00:10:11.679 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:10:15.449 --> 00:10:17.718 position:19% line:89% align:start
[footsteps approaching]

00:10:24.526 --> 00:10:25.893 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[light gasp]
-[exhales]

00:10:26.595 --> 00:10:28.429 position:16% line:89% align:start
Nobody down this hallway.

00:10:28.462 --> 00:10:30.498 position:16% line:83% align:start
I guess they must've gone
the other way.

00:10:30.532 --> 00:10:32.867 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's a guard. What's he...?

00:10:32.900 --> 00:10:34.168 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scoffs]

00:10:34.201 --> 00:10:34.969 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:10:35.002 --> 00:10:35.970 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's that?

00:10:36.003 --> 00:10:38.706 position:16% line:83% align:start
Something forced its way
past this metal gate.

00:10:38.739 --> 00:10:40.741 position:24% line:83% align:start
The prisoner has to
have gone this way!

00:10:40.774 --> 00:10:42.743 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Come in--
-[silenced gunshot]

00:10:45.779 --> 00:10:47.715 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[surprised gasp]
-[surprised gasp]

00:10:48.382 --> 00:10:49.717 position:35% line:89% align:start
[creaking]

00:10:51.553 --> 00:10:52.720 position:24% line:89% align:start
[speechless breath]

00:10:53.921 --> 00:10:55.789 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] Wait, is that...?

00:11:00.461 --> 00:11:01.729 position:33% line:89% align:start
Johngalli A.!

00:11:06.834 --> 00:11:08.736 position:21% line:83% align:start
He came to take care
of us himself!

00:11:09.670 --> 00:11:12.006 position:19% line:83% align:start
Jolyne! Keeping heading
to the window.

00:11:12.039 --> 00:11:14.208 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'll face off against him.
[gasps]

00:11:15.577 --> 00:11:18.647 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's Johngalli A.'s Stand.

00:11:18.679 --> 00:11:20.848 position:16% line:83% align:start
But I thought his attacks
had only been a dream...

00:11:20.881 --> 00:11:23.217 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Die!
-Is this still a dream?!

00:11:27.522 --> 00:11:29.690 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's not! This is happening!

00:11:29.723 --> 00:11:31.025 position:35% line:89% align:start
Time stop!

00:11:38.699 --> 00:11:39.568 position:35% line:89% align:start
The enemy.

00:11:39.601 --> 00:11:40.701 position:21% line:89% align:start
I think there were...

00:11:41.536 --> 00:11:42.403 position:33% line:89% align:start
two of them!

00:11:43.871 --> 00:11:46.273 position:24% line:83% align:start
It conjured visions
for Jolyne and I.

00:11:46.307 --> 00:11:47.642 position:13% line:89% align:start
And even went so far as to

00:11:47.676 --> 00:11:48.976 position:24% line:83% align:start
put Johngalli A.'s
actual Stand

00:11:49.009 --> 00:11:50.411 position:19% line:89% align:start
inside of those dreams.

00:11:50.444 --> 00:11:53.814 position:7% line:83% align:start
Everything had been a set up...
to lead to this.

00:11:53.847 --> 00:11:55.449 position:21% line:83% align:start
Set up precisely for
this moment

00:11:55.482 --> 00:11:56.551 position:30% line:83% align:start
where I'd have
no other options

00:11:56.585 --> 00:11:59.353 position:27% line:83% align:start
but to stop time
to keep my daughter safe!

00:12:00.354 --> 00:12:03.692 position:7% line:89% align:start
Their target... was always me!

00:12:03.724 --> 00:12:06.026 position:7% line:89% align:start
Time is about to start! Jolyne!

00:12:07.261 --> 00:12:08.362 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:12:08.395 --> 00:12:11.398 position:30% line:89% align:start
Ora, ora, ora!

00:12:12.733 --> 00:12:15.102 position:24% line:83% align:start
Looks like you were
one step too late.

00:12:15.135 --> 00:12:18.772 position:33% line:83% align:start
Jotaro Kujo,
how I've waited for this.

00:12:18.806 --> 00:12:20.841 position:13% line:83% align:start
-Wish I could take my time.
-[gasps]

00:12:22.243 --> 00:12:23.110 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squelches]

00:12:27.181 --> 00:12:29.817 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whirring]

00:12:29.850 --> 00:12:32.152 position:38% line:83% align:start
It seems
they were already done.

00:12:32.554 --> 00:12:33.754 position:38% line:89% align:start
Perfect.

00:12:33.787 --> 00:12:36.625 position:13% line:83% align:start
Even the invincible Joestar
couldn't stop me

00:12:36.658 --> 00:12:38.926 position:24% line:83% align:start
from obtaining that
which I wanted!

00:12:38.959 --> 00:12:42.062 position:27% line:83% align:start
You were no match
for the power of Pale Snake!

00:12:42.096 --> 00:12:46.000 position:35% line:83% align:start
[groaning]
The shooter's still up...

00:12:51.338 --> 00:12:52.273 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's a Stand!

00:12:52.306 --> 00:12:54.208 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:12:58.412 --> 00:12:59.847 position:33% line:89% align:start
What the--?!

00:12:59.880 --> 00:13:02.216 position:19% line:83% align:start
But I thought his Stand
was just a dream.

00:13:02.249 --> 00:13:04.653 position:24% line:83% align:start
Anyway, let's move
while he's still reloading.

00:13:04.686 --> 00:13:07.154 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[sinister music playing]
-It's him.

00:13:07.488 --> 00:13:08.523 position:38% line:89% align:start
[oozing]

00:13:14.261 --> 00:13:15.129 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:16.463 --> 00:13:17.298 position:35% line:89% align:start
[squelches]

00:13:24.739 --> 00:13:26.273 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ora!

00:13:27.875 --> 00:13:29.577 position:24% line:89% align:start
[glass clattering]

00:13:30.811 --> 00:13:32.946 position:24% line:83% align:start
There's the shore.
We're almost out!

00:13:32.980 --> 00:13:35.182 position:19% line:89% align:start
[grunts] You go ahead.

00:13:36.350 --> 00:13:37.318 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'll catch up.

00:13:37.351 --> 00:13:39.453 position:21% line:89% align:start
Huh? Let's go! Hurry!

00:13:40.387 --> 00:13:41.255 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on!

00:13:42.289 --> 00:13:43.357 position:41% line:89% align:start
Listen.

00:13:43.390 --> 00:13:45.694 position:27% line:83% align:start
There can only be
one Stand per person.

00:13:45.727 --> 00:13:46.860 position:38% line:89% align:start
So then,

00:13:46.894 --> 00:13:48.630 position:19% line:83% align:start
there were two enemies
from the beginning.

00:13:48.663 --> 00:13:50.230 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:13:50.264 --> 00:13:53.735 position:24% line:83% align:start
Johngalli A.'s one.
The mushy guy, the second...

00:13:53.768 --> 00:13:55.903 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wind howling]

00:14:00.542 --> 00:14:01.942 position:24% line:89% align:start
Take this pendant,

00:14:01.975 --> 00:14:03.944 position:24% line:83% align:start
and get out of here
while you still can.

00:14:03.977 --> 00:14:06.213 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't drop it.

00:14:06.246 --> 00:14:09.049 position:19% line:83% align:start
A transmitter has been
fitted inside of the pendant,

00:14:09.083 --> 00:14:10.819 position:21% line:83% align:start
so they can determine
your location.

00:14:10.851 --> 00:14:12.486 position:27% line:83% align:start
The submarine has
been programmed

00:14:12.520 --> 00:14:15.422 position:24% line:83% align:start
to find and follow
this signal automatically.

00:14:15.456 --> 00:14:17.358 position:13% line:89% align:start
It hones in like a beacon.

00:14:17.391 --> 00:14:19.927 position:27% line:83% align:start
Do you understand
what I'm saying, Jolyne?

00:14:20.528 --> 00:14:21.629 position:21% line:89% align:start
Just go to the shore,

00:14:21.663 --> 00:14:22.797 position:27% line:83% align:start
and the submarine
will come to you.

00:14:22.831 --> 00:14:23.897 position:33% line:89% align:start
Easy as that.

00:14:24.365 --> 00:14:25.232 position:35% line:89% align:start
From there,

00:14:25.265 --> 00:14:27.769 position:16% line:83% align:start
the Speedwagon Foundation
that I mentioned

00:14:27.802 --> 00:14:29.738 position:33% line:83% align:start
will come and
take you somewhere safe.

00:14:29.771 --> 00:14:32.106 position:21% line:89% align:start
[breathes nervously]

00:14:33.006 --> 00:14:34.041 position:33% line:89% align:start
You got that?

00:14:34.441 --> 00:14:35.744 position:38% line:89% align:start
Now, go.

00:14:35.777 --> 00:14:37.645 position:19% line:89% align:start
You mean, this thing...

00:14:38.546 --> 00:14:39.446 position:33% line:89% align:start
Earlier, I...

00:14:40.414 --> 00:14:42.383 position:16% line:89% align:start
I didn't know, but you...

00:14:43.117 --> 00:14:44.451 position:24% line:89% align:start
I want you to know.

00:14:44.485 --> 00:14:46.821 position:30% line:83% align:start
You were always
incredibly important to me.

00:14:46.855 --> 00:14:48.222 position:24% line:89% align:start
[breathing shakily]

00:14:49.356 --> 00:14:50.290 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:14:51.291 --> 00:14:52.226 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:14:52.893 --> 00:14:55.429 position:13% line:89% align:start
You... Hey, what the hell?

00:14:55.462 --> 00:14:57.331 position:13% line:89% align:start
Your chest... It can't be!

00:14:57.965 --> 00:14:59.366 position:21% line:89% align:start
But how? You can't...

00:14:59.400 --> 00:15:03.237 position:35% line:83% align:start
Go. Jolyne,
I'm only bleeding a little.

00:15:03.270 --> 00:15:04.972 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'll catch up to you
in no time.

00:15:05.005 --> 00:15:07.007 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't lie! [gasps]

00:15:07.040 --> 00:15:09.176 position:35% line:83% align:start
All because
you protected me earlier,

00:15:09.209 --> 00:15:12.179 position:21% line:83% align:start
the other enemy took
something away from you!

00:15:12.212 --> 00:15:15.048 position:13% line:83% align:start
And that's why you couldn't
dodge the bullets! Is that it?

00:15:15.617 --> 00:15:17.151 position:27% line:89% align:start
What did he take?

00:15:17.184 --> 00:15:19.486 position:19% line:83% align:start
[gasps] Could it be...
your Stand?

00:15:19.521 --> 00:15:20.354 position:35% line:89% align:start
[gun cocks]

00:15:21.321 --> 00:15:22.456 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-Jolyne!

00:15:25.993 --> 00:15:27.494 position:21% line:89% align:start
[rock music playing]

00:15:29.963 --> 00:15:31.031 position:41% line:89% align:start
No way!

00:15:31.833 --> 00:15:32.700 position:30% line:89% align:start
[annoyed grunt]

00:15:33.500 --> 00:15:35.002 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hey! What is this?

00:15:35.035 --> 00:15:37.404 position:5% line:89% align:start
This thread is... When did it--?

00:15:38.005 --> 00:15:40.240 position:19% line:89% align:start
[grunts] I've got you!

00:15:43.511 --> 00:15:44.378 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:15:45.880 --> 00:15:46.781 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:46.815 --> 00:15:48.616 position:38% line:89% align:start
Be quiet.

00:15:48.650 --> 00:15:49.983 position:13% line:89% align:start
We're getting out of here.

00:15:50.017 --> 00:15:52.319 position:13% line:83% align:start
We're heading to the shore
to make our great escape.

00:15:53.020 --> 00:15:55.657 position:13% line:89% align:start
So don't interfere. Got it?

00:15:56.457 --> 00:15:58.258 position:27% line:89% align:start
Wait, the girl...

00:15:58.292 --> 00:16:00.994 position:21% line:83% align:start
When did she acquire
this kind of Stand?

00:16:01.028 --> 00:16:02.996 position:24% line:83% align:start
A Stand as powerful
as this one

00:16:03.030 --> 00:16:04.666 position:27% line:83% align:start
should've already
been investigated

00:16:04.699 --> 00:16:06.534 position:24% line:83% align:start
before she entered
the facility!

00:16:07.267 --> 00:16:10.070 position:10% line:89% align:start
All right, I'll drop the gun.

00:16:10.538 --> 00:16:10.572 position:38% line:89% align:start
[smirks]

00:16:18.278 --> 00:16:19.146 position:38% line:89% align:start
#[grunts]

00:16:19.614 --> 00:16:20.582 position:27% line:89% align:start
[groans in pain]

00:16:20.615 --> 00:16:21.683 position:41% line:89% align:start
Idiot.

00:16:21.716 --> 00:16:23.984 position:10% line:89% align:start
Simon didn't say, "Drop it."

00:16:24.017 --> 00:16:26.286 position:19% line:83% align:start
I was just checking out
the angles.

00:16:26.320 --> 00:16:27.889 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wanted to make sure
to line up

00:16:27.922 --> 00:16:29.423 position:30% line:83% align:start
the easiest one
to hit you from.

00:16:29.924 --> 00:16:31.258 position:30% line:89% align:start
See, I'd prefer

00:16:31.291 --> 00:16:34.094 position:19% line:83% align:start
if your jaw were facing
a little further to the right.

00:16:34.127 --> 00:16:35.996 position:27% line:83% align:start
If I knew she was
this powerful,

00:16:36.029 --> 00:16:37.799 position:21% line:83% align:start
I would've taken care
of her first

00:16:37.832 --> 00:16:39.567 position:13% line:89% align:start
before going after Jotaro!

00:16:39.601 --> 00:16:42.570 position:27% line:83% align:start
It was my mistake
to make him my first target!

00:16:42.604 --> 00:16:46.106 position:13% line:83% align:start
Is Pale Snake already aware
of this turn of events?

00:16:46.608 --> 00:16:47.842 position:33% line:89% align:start
Jolyne Cujoh.

00:16:47.876 --> 00:16:50.712 position:19% line:83% align:start
There's can be no doubt
that she's Jotaro's daughter!

00:16:50.745 --> 00:16:52.580 position:13% line:89% align:start
A part of the Joestar line!

00:16:53.113 --> 00:16:55.482 position:30% line:89% align:start
Ora, ora, ora!

00:16:56.518 --> 00:16:57.317 position:41% line:89% align:start
Jolyne.

00:16:57.852 --> 00:16:58.620 position:35% line:89% align:start
Earlier...

00:16:59.486 --> 00:17:01.589 position:24% line:83% align:start
when we were stuck
in that dream...

00:17:01.623 --> 00:17:04.291 position:10% line:83% align:start
You said you would stay here
in this prison

00:17:04.324 --> 00:17:06.393 position:19% line:83% align:start
for the sake of a child
that you don't even know.

00:17:06.426 --> 00:17:09.296 position:24% line:83% align:start
He grabbed me as if
he depended on me.

00:17:09.329 --> 00:17:12.065 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's why I'm going back in.

00:17:12.099 --> 00:17:14.802 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Jotaro] I know now
what I saw was just a dream...

00:17:15.837 --> 00:17:16.738 position:35% line:89% align:start
And yet...

00:17:16.771 --> 00:17:18.305 position:10% line:89% align:start
[somber piano music playing]

00:17:20.040 --> 00:17:21.576 position:38% line:89% align:start
[silence]

00:17:24.478 --> 00:17:25.379 position:44% line:89% align:start
Dad!

00:17:25.412 --> 00:17:26.313 position:38% line:89% align:start
Damn it!

00:17:26.346 --> 00:17:27.982 position:27% line:83% align:start
We nearly made it
to the shore!

00:17:28.016 --> 00:17:29.383 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hey, Dad!

00:17:29.851 --> 00:17:30.785 position:41% line:89% align:start
Get up!

00:17:31.886 --> 00:17:33.287 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[dogs barking]
-[guard] Find them!

00:17:33.320 --> 00:17:35.222 position:16% line:89% align:start
Deadly force authorized.

00:17:35.255 --> 00:17:36.958 position:19% line:89% align:start
A guard has been shot!

00:17:36.991 --> 00:17:38.826 position:21% line:83% align:start
The criminal is armed
and dangerous!

00:17:38.860 --> 00:17:40.695 position:24% line:83% align:start
If it comes to it,
shoot to kill!

00:17:41.829 --> 00:17:43.731 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne grunts] Where is it?

00:17:44.298 --> 00:17:45.833 position:24% line:89% align:start
We're at the shore.

00:17:45.867 --> 00:17:47.200 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on.

00:17:47.234 --> 00:17:49.069 position:13% line:89% align:start
That Speedwagon Foundation.

00:17:49.102 --> 00:17:51.806 position:10% line:83% align:start
You say you've got some kind
of connection with them?

00:17:51.839 --> 00:17:53.675 position:30% line:83% align:start
I have no idea
who they are,

00:17:53.708 --> 00:17:56.778 position:21% line:83% align:start
but if a submarine is
really going to come for us,

00:17:56.811 --> 00:17:58.513 position:24% line:83% align:start
then they must have
considerable

00:17:58.546 --> 00:18:01.983 position:21% line:83% align:start
financial assets and
technological capabilities.

00:18:02.016 --> 00:18:04.986 position:33% line:83% align:start
This wound...
hit by a ricochet bullet...

00:18:05.019 --> 00:18:06.353 position:21% line:89% align:start
They'd have to help!

00:18:06.386 --> 00:18:08.121 position:19% line:83% align:start
Surely, they'd be able
to treat it

00:18:08.155 --> 00:18:10.090 position:35% line:83% align:start
better than
any regular doctor!

00:18:10.123 --> 00:18:12.092 position:19% line:89% align:start
Where is the submarine?

00:18:12.125 --> 00:18:15.495 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Where are you?
-[barking]

00:18:15.530 --> 00:18:17.397 position:27% line:89% align:start
[waves splashing]

00:18:19.333 --> 00:18:20.802 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[bubbling]
-[gasps]

00:18:24.839 --> 00:18:26.440 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:26.473 --> 00:18:28.475 position:16% line:83% align:start
So everything you told me
was true.

00:18:29.242 --> 00:18:31.244 position:27% line:83% align:start
The submarine was
already here

00:18:31.278 --> 00:18:32.145 position:24% line:89% align:start
and waiting for us!

00:18:32.179 --> 00:18:33.715 position:24% line:89% align:start
We're in the clear!

00:18:33.748 --> 00:18:34.682 position:33% line:89% align:start
[sudden gasp]

00:18:36.084 --> 00:18:37.384 position:24% line:89% align:start
[speechless breath]

00:18:38.285 --> 00:18:40.588 position:19% line:89% align:start
[somber music playing]

00:18:46.226 --> 00:18:47.494 position:27% line:89% align:start
[exhales shakily]

00:18:49.530 --> 00:18:52.600 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hey! What the hell
are you doing?!

00:18:54.636 --> 00:18:56.203 position:38% line:89% align:start
No way...

00:18:56.236 --> 00:18:58.706 position:21% line:89% align:start
It... It can't be...

00:18:58.740 --> 00:19:00.908 position:24% line:89% align:start
No, there's no way!

00:19:00.942 --> 00:19:02.644 position:21% line:89% align:start
Even if he got shot,

00:19:02.677 --> 00:19:04.211 position:21% line:89% align:start
the wound is shallow.

00:19:04.244 --> 00:19:05.780 position:10% line:89% align:start
None of his vitals were hit!

00:19:06.881 --> 00:19:07.915 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:19:07.949 --> 00:19:10.785 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's not supposed to
be a fatal wound.

00:19:10.818 --> 00:19:11.686 position:41% line:89% align:start
But...

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:14.154 position:21% line:89% align:start
But... Why are you--?

00:19:14.187 --> 00:19:15.422 position:27% line:89% align:start
[sharply inhales]

00:19:15.455 --> 00:19:19.060 position:13% line:83% align:start
Why the hell did your heart
stop beating, Dad?!

00:19:19.093 --> 00:19:22.496 position:24% line:89% align:start
[breathing heavily]

00:19:26.668 --> 00:19:28.201 position:27% line:89% align:start
See? I can tell.

00:19:28.235 --> 00:19:30.104 position:21% line:83% align:start
You've got the blood
of a Joestar.

00:19:30.138 --> 00:19:31.572 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Go.
-[Jolyne crying]

