00:21:58.553 --> 00:21:59.554 position:38% line:89% align:start
I see...

00:22:00.988 --> 00:22:02.590 position:13% line:89% align:start
My mother gave birth to me

00:22:02.623 --> 00:22:04.659 position:33% line:83% align:start
while she was
a prisoner here,

00:22:04.692 --> 00:22:07.394 position:21% line:83% align:start
and I've been hiding
in this prison ever since.

00:22:07.995 --> 00:22:09.931 position:21% line:89% align:start
Your name... tell me.

00:22:09.964 --> 00:22:12.465 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, I'm... Emporio.

00:22:12.900 --> 00:22:14.635 position:38% line:89% align:start
Emporio.

00:22:14.669 --> 00:22:17.071 position:21% line:83% align:start
I was able to survive
